de.ityx.mediatrix.api.client

Interface ICProcessing


  • public interface ICProcessing
    Provides the API to manage processing emails in the mail inbox and operator mode. E.g. loading a next question for the processing in the operator mode.
    How to use:
    API.getClientAPI().getProcessingAPI().prefetch(id);
